	<h1 class="title">落日的时候如果你在海边，有这么一个凉亭会锦上添花</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/161922/small/161922.jpg?1442322894" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">廖婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-12 17:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15929/medium/15929.jpg?1444485082" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="15929" data-title="《落日的时候如果你在海边，有这么一个凉亭会锦上添花》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/15929/medium/15929.jpg?1444485082" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/15929.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
